data.description: How does a 2% RATE BUY DOWN sound? The seller is offering $10,000 in CONCESSIONS to use as you like (rate buy down, closing costs, etc.)! Ask your Realtor for more details. This SPACIOUS 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom gem is nestled on a 1/2-ACRE LOT on a CUL-DE-SAC with great CURB APPEAL and plenty of room for a SHOP in the fully fenced backyard! Inside you’ll find an open concept living area with VAULTED ceilings. Kitchen has a LARGE island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, lots of cabinet space, and a pantry! Front room could be used as a formal dining room or a study. Primary bedroom is downstairs and boasts a HUGE closet, ensuite bathroom with a double vanity sink, soaker tub, and large shower. Upstairs you’ll find the 3 secondary bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, 1 of which is a Jack-and-Jill. The UPSTAIRS BONUS ROOM is large enough to be 2 SEPARATE spaces. Homes also includes commercial grade luxury vinyl, a new dishwasher, Vivint security system, sprinkler system, aerobic septic system, water softener, located in Mustang Schools, and so much more! Schedule your showing to see this one today!
